Even tho it's not beneficial for me to say this, but I would say it again that premium does NOT increase your chances of getting into a boost
Premium is only for convenience (Tier 1 and 2) and style (Tier 3). It is designed to help you sign up to more runs without losing your mind signing up to runs like crazy staring at your monitor

As for how to increase your chances:
There are (on average) 30 runs per hour, meaning 30 tanks, 30 healers, 60 DPS (probably less as some keys require less ppl)
What posters care most about in order (from my experience)
- Your reputation (if they know you as a good booster, they invite you)
- Your class (meta classes this season are way more favorable)
- If you are providing the key
- Your IO
- Your reviews

Also, there are 100-300 signups in good offers, so you should try to sign up as early as possible to appear higher but not as important

In short, be persistent, do everything all levels, let poster know when you 2 3 chest a key and do high DPS, provide key, increase your IO
